title: The Most Valuable Lost Treasure That Still Exists
description: As Imperial Spain transported literal tons of gold from the New World to the motherland, hurricanes sunk much of it to the bottom of the Atlantic. Find out about the most valuable treasure that is likely still out there.    TO HELP OUT THE SHOW  Leave an honest review on iTunes. Your ratings and reviews really help and I read each one.
